The Wine Show - Series 1, Episode 5




From their villa HQ in the Italian hills, Matthew Goode and Matthew Rhys head to Chianti and the former home of Mona Lisa Gherardini, subject of Da Vinci's famous portrait. Expert Joe Fattorini visits the Maule valley to find out how hope can find roots in the vineyards at the epicenter of Chile's devastating 2010 earthquake. Chef Atul Kochhar fires up his tandoor to complement his favourite wine.
